@model FarmMartUI.Areas.Farmer.Models.PlantingViewModel



@*<div class="example-modal" >*@
<div class="modal" role="dialog" id="FormAddCropPlantingDialog" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h4 class="modal-title">Plant Crop</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="box-body">
                @using (Html.BeginForm("PlantCrop", "Planting", FormMethod.Post))
                {
                    @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.Id)
                    @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.FarmCropId)
                    @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                    <div class="form-horizontal">
                        @Html.ValidationSummary(true, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="control-label col-md-3">Planting Date:</label>
                            <div class="col-md-9">
                                @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.DatePlanted, new { @class = "form-control date", @placeholder = "date planted" })
                                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.DatePlanted, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="control-label col-md-3">Due in Months:</label>
                            <div class="col-md-9">
                                @Html.DropDownListFor(model => model.MonthToGrowId, Model.HarvestPeriodDropDown, new { @class = "form-control" })
                                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.MonthToGrowId, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                            </div>
                        </div>
